cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the training and understanding of deep neural networks. It also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it analyzes the activation values of validation images. Additionally, it may fall under the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with neural networks and their behavior. Finally, it may also be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it involves analyzing data and extracting insights.
